OL,6,FDrag artists in are calling for better
OL,7,Fperformance spaces and a dedicated
OL,8,FLGBTQ+ venue.
OL,10,FThey say investment would be needed,
OL,11,Fbut that it could bring social and
OL,12,Ffinancial benefits to the island.
