OL,15,Fhome to 'The Side Door', a bar on
OL,16,FSeaton Place in St Helier that was
OL,17,Fpopular with the LGBTQ+ community.
OL,19,FFormer barman Colin Adams explained:
OL,20,F"The Side Door used to be mobbed.
